name: wide-aai-chests
title: Wide AAI Containers (AAI containers compatibility mod)

description: Provides graphics for AAI containers compatibility. This mod does nothing by itself, requires Wide Containers to function, and purely exists to have a separate restricted mod license. This specific mod is not open source, please read the mod license! Thanks to Earendel for allowing modification and use of AAI containers assets.
